  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this non-interventional, observational study is to assess the effectiveness
      and patient reported outcome of adalimumab in patients with moderate to severe psoriasis in
      real world clinical practice in China.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
